  "link": "http://cn.engadget.com/2013/07/26/google-glass-developer-kit-android-dev-kit/", 
  "description": "<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"cn.engadget.com/2013/07/26/google-glass-developer-kit-android-dev-kit/\"><img src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/07/glass-headshot-2013-04-29-619.jpg\" style=\"margin: 4px;\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n在 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/IO2013/\">I/O 2013</a> 之时，Google 曾指出为 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/Glass/\">Glass</a> 专设的<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2013/04/15/google-glass-api-documentation-now-live-glassware-sample-code/\">开发者工具</a>快要推出，让到开发者可以更方便地为其开发程式，不过似乎目前的进度仍然与推出日子有一点距离呢。Glass 团队的其中一位工程师 Alain Vongsouvanh 最近就在 Google+ 上指出，他们仍在制作 Glass 的 SDK，各位开发者想为其开发程式的话，则鼓励使用现有的 Android SDK（API Level 15）。为了使到开发者们可以起步得更快，他们已公布了秒表、水平仪和指南针的代码样本，及后他们不但会公布更多样本，在 Glass APK 推出之时更会教导大家如何移植 app 呢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2013/07/26/google-glass-developer-kit-android-dev-kit/\">Engadget</a><br />\n引用来源：<a href=\"https://plus.google.com/u/0/+AlainVongsouvanh/posts/HsVea4ZR8pH\">Alain Vongsouvanh（Google+）</a>、<a href=\"https://developers.google.com/glass/gdk\">Google Glass Development Kit</a>、<a href=\"https://github.com/googleglass\">Glass GitHub</a><br />\n更多报导：<a href=\"http://techcrunch.com/2013/07/26/google-asks-glass-developers-to-start-working-on-android-based-apps-ahead-of-glass-development-kit-launch/\">TechCrunch</a></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/07/26/google-glass-developer-kit-android-dev-kit/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20678589/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/07/26/google-glass-developer-kit-android-dev-kit/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
